narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take this class! It is a fun, somewhat rigorous acting class that allows you to do a lot of scenes. Joan is also excellent.

It's a good beginning scene class. You work on four very different scenes throughout the course. If you're new to acting, this could be a really helpful and fun class. If you've already had extensive training, this class could hurt more than it helps.
